# --- Ralph build harness: transient scratch only ---
# The backlog (.harness/tracking/TASKS.json) and per-task worklog/specs ARE committed; only the loop's
# transient per-run scratch + the private ideas inbox are ignored.
.harness/worklog/.result
.harness/worklog/.claude-out
.harness/worklog/.claude-out.jsonl
.harness/worklog/.current.json
.harness/worklog/STATUS.md
.harness/worklog/*.audit.md
.harness/worklog/.failures.buf
.harness/worklog/.last-push-ts
# The ideas inbox is a PRIVATE, transient capture scratchpad (raw, unfleshed ideas). The mechanism
# travels via .harness/CLAUDE.md; each repo grows its own private inbox.
.harness/tracking/IDEAS.jsonl
# /convert-ideas scratch: a per-unit agent writes its decided task(s) to its own uniquely-named
# file here (zero lock contention during interview/shaping); the Stage 3 consolidation pass reads,
# allocates ids, and deletes them. Never committed — see .harness/CLAUDE.md and the
# implementation-harness plugin's convert-ideas skill.
.harness/.pending-tasks/
# /convert-ideas scratch: a per-unit agent blocked on a genuine open question (it has no
# AskUserQuestion — that's main-thread-only) writes its questions here durably BEFORE ending its
# turn, so the question survives even if the coordinating session ends before relaying it to the
# owner. Deleted once the unit is unblocked and finishes shaping. Never committed.
.harness/.pending-questions/
# Private seed data pasted alongside an idea (e.g. spreadsheet dumps) — same privacy as the inbox.
.harness/perfume-seed-data.tsv
# atomic-write temps for the owner-owned overlays + TASKS.json.
.harness/tracking/TASKS.json.tmp
.harness/tracking/reviews.json.tmp*
# Visual-check screenshots (scripts/visual-check.mjs) — regenerated each run, never committed.
scripts/visual-out/
